Not fully understanding that those same feet would be used and abused would be bruised and beat for our sake.

00:28:44.581 --> 00:28:52.274
Not fully understanding that the next time she would see him, his blood would be dripping from the cross.

00:28:58.082 --> 00:29:19.353
And yet she poured out that whole bottle of oil on Jesus as an offering of her faith, an offering of her love, an offering of her expectation that God is who God says God is.

00:29:23.520 --> 00:29:25.202
A sacrifice.

00:29:31.202 --> 00:29:31.963
She wept.

00:29:34.528 --> 00:29:38.635
She could have done it privately, but she did it publicly.

00:29:38.675 --> 00:29:41.119
She wept.

00:29:42.862 --> 00:29:52.018
She humbled herself in such a way that she got on the floor and she cleaned his feet with her hair.

00:30:01.698 --> 00:30:02.819
What is your offering?

00:30:06.244 --> 00:30:09.828
What is your offering?

00:30:13.733 --> 00:30:15.856
What will you bring to Jesus?

00:30:20.361 --> 00:30:22.344
What will you say?

00:30:22.404 --> 00:30:27.210
God, I know I've been kind of just half doing this.

00:30:29.773 --> 00:30:30.674
I'm all in.

00:30:34.466 --> 00:30:39.586
God, I don't know how I'm going to do it, but I'm going to do it.

00:30:39.646 --> 00:30:45.650
You've been saying that you want me to, so I'm finally going to do it.

00:30:49.122 --> 00:30:51.246
I'm gonna show up for the least of these.

00:30:51.266 --> 00:30:53.469
I'm gonna show up in the sanctuary.

00:30:53.509 --> 00:30:55.573
I'm gonna show up for you, Lord.

00:30:55.613 --> 00:30:57.536
I'm gonna show up for the kids.

00:30:57.556 --> 00:30:59.700
I'm gonna show up for society.

00:31:00.301 --> 00:31:05.289
I am going to bring an unlikely offering to God.

00:31:05.309 --> 00:31:15.506
And don't forget,

00:31:18.338 --> 00:31:26.947
The Luke text says, and you shall go in peace.

00:31:35.457 --> 00:31:35.977
Want peace?

00:31:40.782 --> 00:31:42.484
It's going to take a sacrificial offering.

00:31:46.709 --> 00:31:47.730
You want peace?

00:31:49.122 --> 00:31:53.388
You're going to have to get real and vulnerable in the presence of the Almighty God.

00:31:56.813 --> 00:31:59.276
You want a lint that actually means something?

00:32:06.105 --> 00:32:18.322
It's going to take a gift of love, devotion, or generosity that may seem unexpected, unusual,

00:32:18.882 --> 00:32:20.023
or unlikely.

00:32:26.891 --> 00:32:30.396
What shall it be?

00:32:34.260 --> 00:32:40.287
In the name of the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit, we pray.

00:32:42.189 --> 00:32:42.770
Amen.
